FBIS3-3688 "drchi056_j_94004" FBIS-CHI-94-056 Document Type:Daily Report 18 Mar 1994 Latin America & Caribbean President Arrives in Shanghai OW1803143094 Beijing XINHUA in English 1317 GMT 18 Mar 94 OW1803143094 Beijing XINHUA Language: English Article Type:BFN [Text] Shanghai, March 18 (XINHUA) -- Ecuador President Sixto Duran Ballen arrived here this afternoon by air from Tokyo to start a state visit to China. His entourage includes his wife, foreign minister, finance minister, agriculture and livestock minister, commander general of the army, and some entrepreneurs. On behalf of Shanghai Mayor Huang Ju, Vice-Mayor Xu Kuangdi welcomed the ecuador president. This evening, Sixto Duran Ballen toured the city and the bund.
